DISPLAY AND VISIBILITY

| Property             | Hidden? | Takes up Space? | Removed from Flow? |
| -------------------- | ------- | --------------- | ------------------ |
| `display: none`      | ✅ Yes  | ❌ No          | ✅ Yes             |
| `visibility: hidden` | ✅ Yes  | ✅ Yes         | ❌ No               |

